Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Lee%20reiterated%20his%20view%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-fundstrat-price-target-increase-sp500-artificial-intelligence-2023-7%5C%22%3Ecould%20hit%20a%20new%20all-time-high%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20end%20the%20year%20at%204%2C825%2C%20implying%20an%208%25%20increase%20from%20current%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20largely%20due%20to%20cooling%20prices%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20Lee%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-is-inflation-looking-consumer-price-index-june-data-2023-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCore%2520CPI%2520edged%2520up%2520by%2Cmonth%2520from%2520March%2520to%2520May.%5C%22%3EJune%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Headline%20inflation%20eased%20to%203%25%20and%20core%20inflation%20eased%20to%204.8%25%2C%20in%20line%20with%20Lee's%20estimate%20for%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20three%20big%20tailwinds%20boosting%20it%20on%20the%20path%20to%20new%20record%20highs%2C%20Lee%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Inflation%20keeps%20cooling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20seen%20in%20the%20June%20CPI%20report%20are%20%26quot%3Blikely%20repeatable%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said%2C%20predicting%20a%200.2%25%20price%20drop%20in%20the%20July%20and%20August%20core%20inflation%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20The%20Fed%20pulls%20back%20on%20interest%20rate%20hikes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFed%20officials%20have%20raised%20interest%20rates%20from%20zero%20to%20more%20than%205%25%20in%20the%20last%20year%20to%20lower%20inflation%2C%20a%20move%20that%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20stocks%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20crumbling%20inflation%20gives%20the%20central%20bank%20leeway%20to%20pause%20further%20hikes%20or%20even%20cut%20interest%20rates%2C%20Lee%20suggested%2C%20especially%20considering%20