ber%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Radio%20Free%20Europe.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20if%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20next%20year%2C%20the%20first%20F-16s%20fly%20in%20Ukrainian%20air%2C%20piloted%20by%20Ukrainian%20pilots%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20according%20to%20the%20schedule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20mentioning%20a%20specific%20time%20frame%2C%20Ukraine's%20top%20military%20general%2C%20Valery%20Zaluzhny%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F06%2F30%2Fvalery-zaluzhny-ukraine-general-interview%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20that%20even%20the%20slow%20progress%20in%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive%20was%20extraordinary%20given%20its%20limited%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20admonished%20observers%20who%20were%20expecting%20quick%20results%20as%20unrealistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaluzhny%20told%20The%20Post.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20show%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20watching%20and%20betting%20on%20or%20anything.%20Every%20day%2C%20every%20meter%20is%20given%20by%20blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20being%20fully%20supplied%2C%20these%20plans%20are%20not%20feasible%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20are%20being%20carried%20out.%20Yes%2C%20maybe%20not%20as%20fast%20as%20the%20participants%2C%20the%20observers%2C%20would%20like%2C%20but%20that%20is%20their%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20aggressively%20pressed%20its%20case%20to%20join%20NATO%2C%20a%20yearslong%20aim%20which%20existing%20members%20have%20been%20hesitant%20to%20attach%20to%20a%20particular%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20said%20in%202008%20that%20Ukraine%20could%20join%20at%20a%20future%20date%2C%20but%20declined%20its%20September%202022%20request%20for%20%26quot%