ed%20by%20stable%20margins%2C%20new%20generation%20business%20opportunities%20and%20increase%20in%20pricing%20power%20due%20to%20moderation%20in%20USD%2C%20as%20latest%20US%20inflation%20is%20fast%20approaching%20the%20Fed's%20target%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinod%20Nair%2C%20Head%20of%20Research%20at%20Geojit%20Financial%20Services%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20Sensex%20pack%2C%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20Infosys%2C%20Bajaj%20Finserv%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20Wipro%20and%20Bajaj%20Finance%20were%20among%20the%20major%20gainers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETCS%20climbed%202.47%20per%20cent%20a%20day%20after%20announcing%20its%20June%20quarter%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20largest%20IT%20services%20company%20on%20Wednesday%20reported%20a%2016.83%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20June%20quarter%20net%20profit%20to%20Rs%2011%2C074%20crore%20but%20sounded%20circumspect%20about%20growth%20prospects%20for%20the%20fiscal%20due%20to%20market%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPower%20Grid%2C%20Maruti%2C%20NTPC%2C%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20Hindustan%20Unilever%20and%20Nestle%20were%20among%20the%20laggards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20showed%20retail%20inflation%20rose%20to%20a%20three-month%20high%20in%20June%20on%20rising%20prices%20of%20kitchen%20essentials%2C%20while%20the%20factory%20output%20expanded%20at%20a%20faster%20pace%20of%205.2%20per%20cent%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetail%20inflation%20based%20on%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20(CPI)%20increased%20to%204.81%20per%20cent%20in%20June%20after%20declining%20for%20four%20months%20in%20a%20row%20but%20remained%20within%20the%20comfort%20zone%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20broad%20market%20was%20trading%20positively%20at%20all-time%20high%20levels%20in%20anticipation%20of%20buoyant%20Q1%20results%20and%20low%20volatility%20(VIX).%20However%2C%20a%20mixed%20start%20to%20bank%20earnings%2