tions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELater%20today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20meet%20the%20French%20Prime%20Minister%20Elisabeth%20Borne%20%E2%80%93%20who%20received%20him%20at%20the%20airport%20--%20visit%20the%20Senate%20and%20meet%20President%20of%20the%20Senate%20Gerrad%20Larcher.%20The%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20entire%20French%20political%20leadership%20indicates%20a%20shared%20commitment%20to%20the%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAround%2011%20PM%20Indian%20time%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20address%20an%20Indian%20community%20event%20at%20the%20iconic%20La%20Seine%20Musicale.%20Later%2C%20he%20would%20attend%20a%20private%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20the%20French%20President%20at%20his%20residence.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETomorrow%2C%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20celebrations%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20bilateral%20talks.%20A%20range%20of%20topics%20is%20on%20agenda%2C%20including%20cooperation%20in%20the%20spheres%20of%20security%2C%20technology%2C%20counterterrorism%2C%20cybersecurity%2C%20climate%20change%20and%20space.%20The%20visit%20will%20conclude%20with%20a%20grand%20state%20banquet%20at%20the%20iconic%20Louvre%20Museum.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20departing%20for%20France%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20he%20would%20hold%20wide-ranging%20discussions%20with%C2%A0%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20to%20take%20forward%20the%20time-tested%20partnership.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BRooted%20in%20deep%20trust%20and%20commitment%2C%20our%20two%20countries%20cooperate%20closely%20across%20various%20domains%20including%20defence%2C%20space%2C%20civil%20nuclear%2C%20blue%20economy%2C%20trade%2C%20investment%2C%20education%2C%20culture%20and%20people%20to%20people%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20few%20big-ticket%20announcements%20are%20expected%20during%20the%20visit%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20acquisition%20of%20another%2026%20Rafale%20jets%20and%20three%20Scorpene%20submarines.%20The%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Committee%20headed%20by%20Union%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20cleared%20the%20process%20and%20negotiations%20are%20likely%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBastille%20Day%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Fete%20Nationale%20Francaise%2C%20is%20celebrated%20on%20July%2014%20and%20commemorates%20the%20storming%20of%20the%20French%20prison%20in%201789%2C%20which%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20French%20Revolution.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Indian%20tri-services%20are%20going%20to%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20tomorrow's%20celebration.%20A%20269-member%20contingent%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20Navy%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%20will%20march%20alongside%20their%20French%20counterparts%20at%20the%20grand%20parade.%20The%20alliance%20between%20the%20two%20armies%20go%20back%20to%20World%20War%201.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrance%20has%20been%20one%20of%20India's%20closest%20allies%20in%20Europe%20for%20decades.%20It%20was%20the%20only%20country%20not%20to%20impose%20sanctions%20on%20New%20Delhi%20after%20India%20conducted%20nuclear%20tests%20in%201998%20and%20went%20on%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20staunchest%20defence%20partners.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20India%20has%20replaced%20its%20aging%20Russian%20fleet%20with%20French%20Mirages%2C%20Rafales%20and%20Scorpenes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrom%20France%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20visit%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20meet%20President%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20ruler%20of%20Abu%20Dhabi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689249120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fh6vk87oc_narendra-modi-france-bastille_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-lands-in-paris-rafale-jets-bastille-day-celebrations-in-focus-4203771%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20in%20Paris%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20that%20will%20firm%20up%20crucial%20de