r%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20advanced%204.5th%20generation%20fighter%20jets%20will%20be%20primarily%20deployed%20on%20India's%20Indigenous%20aircraft%20carrier%20INS%20Vikrant.%20The%20deal%20represents%20a%20significant%20development%20in%20the%20Navy's%20fighter%20fleet%20because%20the%20Russian-origin%20MiG-29K%20jets%20have%20been%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20fighter%20arm%20since%20the%20British-made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiannavy.nic.in%2Fcontent%2Findian-navy-bid-adieu-sea-harrier-fighters%5C%22%3ESea%20Harriers%20were%20phased%20out%20in%202016%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20almost%2030%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202015%20report%2C%20the%20Comptroller%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20highlighted%20issues%20with%20the%20MiG-29K's%20airframe%2C%20its%20RD%20MK-33%20engine%20and%20its%20fly-by-wire%20system%2C%20and%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BAircraft%20were%20being%20technically%20accepted%20despite%20having%20discrepancies%2Fanomalies.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20said%20the%20serviceability%20of%20the%20MiG-29K%20(the%20single-seat%20variant)%20was%20low%2C%20%26quot%3Branging%20from%2015.93%20per%20cent%20to%2037.63%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20MiG-29%20K%20UB%20(twin-seat%20trainer)%2C%20it%20ranged%20from%20%26quot%3B21.30%20per%20cent%20to%2047.14%20per%20cent%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nation's%20auditor%20warned%20that%20the%20issues%20with%20MiG-29K%2FKUB%20would%20further%20reduce%20the%20operational%20life%20of%20the%20fighter%20from%206%2C000%20hours%20or%2025%20years%2C%20whichever%20is%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20had%20initially%20pitched%20for%2057%20fighter%20jets%20but%20is%20buying%20only%2026%20in%20this%20multi-billion-dollar%20deal%2C%20which%20would%20be%20finalised%20during%20PM%20Modi's%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20anticipated%20that%20a%20squadron%20of%20the%20Rafale%20M%20would%20be%20deployed%20on%20INS%20Vikrant%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20would%20be%20used%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%20(HAL)%20is%20d%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-developed-this-futuristic-variant-of-tejas-could-match-iafs-rafale-jets-2159016%5C%22%3Eeveloping%20a%20twin-engine%20deck-based%20fighter%20(TEDBF)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20powerful%20derivative%20of%20the%20LCA%20Tejas%2C%20which%20will%20be%20inducted%20to%20replace%20the%20ageing%20MiG-29K%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20milestone%2C%20the%20naval%20variant%20of%20the%20Tejas%20landed%20on%20INS%20Vikrant%2C%20but%20unlike%20its%20Air%20Force%20variant%2C%20which%20is%20operational%20in%20different%20squadrons%2C%20the%20formal%20induction%20of%20this%20variant%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20TEDBF%20into%20the%20Naval%20air%20arm%20will%20take%20a%20few%20more%20years%2C%20the%20Rafale%20M%20deal%20holds%20significant%20importance%20in%20meeting%20the%20operational%20needs%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689247680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fpbaos6f_rafale-marine-fighter-jet-rafale-m-fighter-jet-website-photo_625x300_02_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-in-france-rafale-deal-indian-navy-rafale-m-significance-of-rafale-boost-for-navys-fighter-fleet-explained-4203994%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20France%20marks%20a%20significant%20moment%20in%20bilateral%20relations%20as%20India%20plans%20to%20buy%2026%20Rafale%20M%20(Marine)%20fighter%20jets%20and%20three%20Scorpene%20class%20submarines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-in-france-rafale-deal-indian-navy-rafale-m-significance-of-rafale-boost-for-navys-fighter-fleet-explained-4203994