20been%20astonishing.%20According%20to%20Japanese%20intelligence%20in%20February%2C%2020%20Russian%20generals%20have%20been%20killed%20so%20far%20in%20the%20war%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FSpotlight%2FComment%2FDeaths-in-Russia-s-top-brass-unnerve-India-and-China%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENikkei%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20behind%20the%20high%20Russian%20death%20toll%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIan%20Williams%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20said%20that%20problems%20with%20Russia's%20command%20structure%2C%20and%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20the%20Storm%20Shadow%2C%20were%20among%20the%20factors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20reason%20many%20high-level%20Russian%20officers%20have%20died%20through%20much%20of%20the%20war%20is%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20front%2C%20due%20to%20the%20Russian%20military's%20problems%20with%20command%20and%20control%20and%20delegation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rigid%20Russian%20command%20structure%20means%20that%20junior%20officers%20often%20feel%20unable%20to%20make%20independent%20decisions%2C%20and%20morale%20on%20the%20front%20line%20is%20said%20to%20be%20poor%2C%20meaning%20senior%20officers%20take%20direct%20control%20and%20expose%20themselves%20to%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoor%20Russian%20communications%20systems%20also%20played%20a%20role.%20One%20Russian%20general%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20early%20months%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fpolitics%2Fworld%2Fnews%2Fukraine-killed-a-russian-general-after-he-made-an-unsecured-call-that-gave-away-his-location-report-says%2Farticleshow%2F90294071.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafter%20he%20using%20a%20regular%20cellphone%20which%20was%20easily%20traced%20using%20cellphone%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Kremlin%20has%20