C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20likely%20to%20host%20a%20dinner%20for%20opposition%20party%20leaders%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20meet%20on%20July%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20will%20crystallise%20how%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20national%20party%20in%20the%20opposition%20%E2%80%93%20sees%20its%20own%20role%20in%20solidifying%20the%20anti-BJP%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fpatna-amidst-aap-congress-sparring-16-opposition-parties-vow-to-unitedly-fight-the-bjp%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3E16%20Parties%20Vow%20to%20Unitedly%20Fight%20the%20BJP%2C%20Hark%20Back%20to%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Historic%20Role%20in%20Opposition%20Unity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20four%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exercise%20to%20unite%20opposition%20parties%2C%20which%20began%20about%2011%20months%20ago%2C%20has%20witnessed%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20the%20stature%20of%20four%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20boss%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%E2%80%99s%20role%20assumes%20importance%20considering%20the%20open%20secret%20that%20his%20Bengal%20counterpart%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20that%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20too%20is%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Nitish%20has%20made%20efforts%20to%20get%20these%20two%20parties%20with%20conflicting%20interests%20in%20respective%20states%20to%20join%20the%20common%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20outdone%20his%20own%20reputation%20in%20displaying%20extraordinary%20political%20acumen%20in%20dealing%20with%20tricky%20situations%20within%20his%20own%20party%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-shows-his-mettle-and-guile-in-parliament%5C%22%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%20Shows%20His%20Mettle%20and%20Guile%20in%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20brought%20victory%20for%20his%20party%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20then%20sorted%20out%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Karnataka%20CM%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%20D.K.%20Shivakumar.%20He%20has%2C%20ostensibly%2C%20worked%20to%20maintain%20a%20delicate%20balance%20between%20the%20Rajasthan%20CM%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20his%20rival%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20and%20done%20the%20same%20between%20Chhattisgarh%20CM%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20his%20rival%20turned%20deputy%20T.%20S.%20Singh%20Deo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20losing%20his%20MP%20role%20following%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20continuous%20machinations%20against%20him%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20has%20made%20efforts%20in%20connecting%20with%20the%20masses%2C%20particularly%20agriculturists.%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20draws%20comparisons%20with%20his%20grandmother%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20photographs%20showing%20him%20with%20the%20farm%20workers%20in%20muddy%20fields%20must%20add%20to%20the%20discomfiture%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20often%20draws%20flak%20for%20his%20ostentation%20and%20extravagance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20was%20in%20jail%20for%20over%20four%20years%20ever%20since%202017.%20He%20underwent%20a%20kidney%20transplant%20after%20he%20procured%20bail.%20But%20when%20he%20participated%20in%20a%20political%20activity%20at%20Patna%20on%20June%2023%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years%2C%20he%20stole%20the%20show%20with%20the%20assertion%20%E2%80%93%20in%20his%20inimitable%20style%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20would%20%E2%80%98fix%E2%80%99%20Modi.%20He%20made%20the%20audience%20laugh%20with%20his%20characteristic%20light%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20BJP%20Gears%20Up%20for%202024%20Polls%2C%20Thrust%20Will%20Be%20on%20Modi%20as%20Statesman%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-2024-polls-narendra-modi-statesman%5C%22%3EAs%20BJP%20Gears%20Up%20for%202024%20Polls%2C%20Thrust%20Will%20Be%20on%20Modi%20as%20Statesman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20BJP%20has%20stepped%20up%20using%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20and%20huge%20financial%20resources%20at%20its%20command%20is%20visible%20in%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20several%20of%20his%20colleagues%20in%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20joining%20its%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Pawar%20and%20four%20others%20had%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20hot%20on%20their%20heels%20in%20connection%20with%20cases%20of%20scams%20and%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20current%20CM%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%2040%20MLAs%20had%20defected%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20to%20form%20a%20BJP%20supported%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Goa%20and%20several%20other%20northeast%20states%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20succeeded%20in%20engineering%20large%20scale%20defections%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20to%20replace%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20constantly%20tried%20to%20split%20the%20JD(U)%20in%20Bihar.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-bihar-central-agencies-ajit-pawar-tejashwi-nitish%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Eit%20has%20failed%20with%20Nitish%20keeping%20his%20eyes%20peeled%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1689317750330000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0Byq_VEmSgAhhfs6-cZGoS%5C%22%3ENalin%20Verma%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20social%20anthropology.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689246055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13160506%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-4.04.26.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbangalore-opposition-meeting-nitish-lalu-rahul-mallikarjun-kharge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20meeting%20will%20crystallise%20how%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20national%20party%20in%20the%20opposition%20%E2%80%93%20sees%20its%20own%20role%20in%20solidifying%20the%20anti-BJP%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbangalore-opposition-meeting-nitish-lalu-rahul-mallikarjun-kharge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Millions%20of%20users%20are%20flocking%20to%20an%20AI-powered%20chatbot%20that%20lets%20them%20chat%20with%20famous%20figures%20like%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Mario%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225306%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20laughing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6444f392b6607200180d278f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20has%20been%20giving%20away%20Twitter%20Blue%20checkmarks%20for%20free%3Cp%3EODD%20ANDERSEN%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECharacter.AI%20lets%20users%20chat%20with%20and%20create%20bots%20based%20on%20famous%20figures%20throughout%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20app%20had%20been%20downloaded%20more%20than%205%20million%20times%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPopular%20figures%20on%20the%20platform%20include%20Mario%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20and%20Albert%20Einstein.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20launch%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%20November%2C%20AI-powered%20chatbots%20have%20been%20flooding%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20platform%2C%20Character.AI%2C%20says%20it's%20doing%20things%20differently%20from%20its%20competitors.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20instead%20of%20delivering%20responses%20in%20a%20consistent%20voice%20or%20a%20set%20of%20pre-programmed%20personas%2C%20users%20can%20converse%20with%20and%20create%20chatbots%20based%20on%20famous%20figures%20throughout%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20cofounded%20by%20former%20Google%20Brain%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-characterai-ceo-noam-shazeer-chatbot-2023-4%5C%22%3EDaniel%20De%20Freitas%20and%20Noam%20Shazeer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20May%2C%20they%20launched%20an%20app%20to%20accompany%20the%20website%20version%20of%20the%20platform%2C%20which%20the%20company%20says%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F05%2F31%2Fcharacter-ai-the-a16z-backed-chatbot-startup-tops-1-7m-installs-in-first-week%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edownloaded%201.7%20million%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20app%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20its%20user%20base.%20By%20July%2C%20Character.AI%20had%20been%20downloaded%20more%20than%205%20million%20times%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-07%2Fcharacter-ai-chatbots-are-tech-s-weirdest-1-billion-hit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20chatbot's%20appeal%20is%20the%20range%20and%20creativity%20of%20its%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AI%20version%20of%20Albert%20Einstein%20is%20one%20of%20the%20more%20popular%20figures%2C%20with%20the%20chatbot%20responding%20to%20around%201.6%20million%20messages%20so%20far%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%20A%20character%20based%20on%20the%20Nintendo%2064%20version%20of%20Mario%20has%20received%2036%20million%20messages%20from%20users%2C%20the%20publication%20added.%20Other%20popular%20characters%20include%20a%20version%20of%20Micheal%20Jackson%2C%20Tony%20Stark%2C%20and%20Socrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20also%20a%20key%20figure%20on%20the%20platform%20and%20there%20are%20reportedly%20around%20a%20dozen%20versions%20of%20the%20outspoken%20billionaire%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bcheese%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bkind%2C%20gassy%2C%20proud%26quot%3B%20unicorn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20has%20faced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2dd88b0bb6d46fa7509f307e63d0c8935e5e860883a8684258f07cb6edb9c8d5%26postID%3D64afbff63295ef564526c7e5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Ffeed%252Fupdate%252Furn%253Ali%253Aactivity%253A7077458414246776832%252F%253FupdateEntityUrn%253Durn%25253Ali%25253Afs_feedUpdate%25253A%252528V2%25252Curn%25253Ali%25253Aactivity%25253A7077458414246776832%252529%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20ethics%20of%20mimicking%20the%20personas%20of%20famous%20people%20or%20using%20copyrighted%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Character.AI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharacterai-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-mimics-mario-elon-musk-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689245893000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64afe044c22d1a0019453fd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharacterai-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-mimics-mario-elon-musk-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Character.AI%20has%20around%20a%20dozen%20versions%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20that%20users%20can%20chat%20with%2C%20including%20a%20%26quot%3Bkind%2C%20gassy%2C%20proud%26quot%3B%20unicorn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharacterai-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-mimics-mario-elon-musk-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman%20Rushdie%20Speaks%20Of%20%5C%22Crazy%20Dreams%5C%22%20About%20Knife%20Attack%20In%20New%20York%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESalman%20Rushdie%20has%20spoken%20for%20the%20first%20time%20about%20having%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20dreams%26quot%3B%20following%20the%20near-fatal%20knife%20attack%20on%20him%20in%20New%20York%20in%20August%20last%20year%2C%20which%20has%20left%20the%20Mumbai-born%20author%20blind%20in%20one%20eye%2C%20and%20working%20with%20a%20therapist%20to%20help%20him%20process%20the%20mental%20impact%20of%20the%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2076-year-old%20Booker%20Prize-winning%20author%20was%20on%20stage%20almost%20a%20year%20ago%20when%20he%20was%20stabbed%20up%20to%2010%20times%20by%20the%20suspect%20Hadi%20Matar%2C%20who%20is%20being%20held%20in%20prison%20for%20attempted%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20BBC%20this%20week%2C%20Rushdie%20said%20he%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Btwo%20minds%26quot%3B%20about%20whether%20to%20face%20his%20alleged%20attacker%2C%20who%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%2C%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20very%20good%20therapist%20who%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20do.%20I%20have%20crazy%20dreams%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20British-American%20novelist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20changes%20his%20plea%20to%20guilty%20then%20actually%20there's%20not%20a%20trial%2C%20there's%20just%20a%20sentencing%2C%20and%20it%20may%20well%20be%20that%20then%20my%20presence%20isn't%20required.%20I'm%20in%20two%20minds%20about%20it.%20There's%20one%20bit%20of%20me%20that%20actually%20wants%20to%20go%20and%20stand%20on%20the%20court%20and%20look%20at%20him%20and%20there's%20another%20bit%20of%20me%20that%20just%20can't%20be%20bothered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20very%20high%20opinion%20of%20him.%20And%20I%20think%20what%20is%20important%20to%20me%20now%20is%20that%20you're%20able%20to%20find%20life%20continuing.%20I'm%20more%20engaged%20with%20the%20business%20of%2C%20you%20know%2C%20getting%20on%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20if%20he%20plans%20to%20attend%20Matar's%20trial%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injuries%20from%20the%20attack%20resulted%20in%20damage%20to%20his%20liver%2C%20loss%20of%20vision%20in%20one%20eye%20and%20a%20paralysed%20hand%20caused%20by%20nerve%20damage%20to%20his%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20human%20body%20has%20an%20amazing%20capacity%20to%20heal.%20And%20so%20I'm%20fortunate%20to%20be%20well%20on%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20author%20of%20'Midnight's%20Children'%20who%20says%20he%20feels%20physically%20%26quot%3Bmore%20or%20less%20OK%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20put%20on%20a%20ventilator%20and%20spent%20six%20weeks%20in%20hospital%20after%20being%20stabbed%20up%20to%2010%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERushdie%20is%20now%20writing%20a%20book%20about%20the%20near-fatal%20stabbing%20incident%20as%20a%20means%20of%20processing%20what%20he%20has%20been%20through.%20In%20the%20virtual%20interview%2C%20he%20told%20the%20BBC%20it%20won't%20be%20more%20than%20a%20%26quot%3Bcouple%20of%20hundred%20pages%26quot%3B%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20colossal%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20and%2C%20until%20I%20deal%20with%20that%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20take%20seriously%20anything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20American%20author%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20New%20York%2C%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20fatwa%20by%20Iranian%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Khomeini%20for%20his%20controversial%20novel%20'The%20Satanic%20Verses'%20issued%20over%2030%20years%20ago%20and%20has%20had%20several%20death%20threats%20over%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20latest%20book%2C%20'Victory%20City'%2C%20was%20finished%20just%20before%20the%20attack%20in%20August%20last%20year%20and%20has%20been%20well-received%20by%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689245340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F16q4apko_salman-rushdie-first-interview-post-attack-650_650x400_06_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsalman-rushdie-speaks-of-crazy-dreams-about-knife-attack-in-new-york-4203749%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Salman%20Rushdie%2C%20the%20Booker%20Prize-winning%20author%2C%20was%20on%20stage%20almost%20a%20year%20ago%20when%20he%20was%20stabbed%20up%20to%2010%20times%20by%20Hadi%20Matar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsalman-rushdie-speaks-of-crazy-dreams-about-knife-attack-in-new-york-4203749%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsalman-rushdie-speaks-of-crazy-dreams-about-knife-attack-in-new-york-4203749%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsalman-rushdie-speaks-of-crazy-dreams-about-knife-attack-in-new-york-4203749%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Peter%20Moffat%20to%20Adapt%20True%20Life%20Auschwitz%20Outbreak%20Novel%20%E2%80%98The%20Escape%20Artist%