%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fhollywood-actors-poised-to-strike-as-deadline-for-deal-passes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20Hackers%20Breached%20US%20Government%20Emails%20Via%20Microsoft%20Cloud%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20blog%20posts%20by%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20company%20disclosed%20that%20a%20China-based%20hacking%20group%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BStorm-0558%26quot%3B%20have%20secretly%20accessed%20email%20accounts%20at%20around%2025%20organisations%2C%20including%20at%20least%20two%20US%20government%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2023%2F07%2F12%2Fmicrosoft-hack-china%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Gina%20Raimondo%20is%20the%20only%20known%20Cabinet-level%20official%20to%20have%20their%20account%20compromised%20in%20the%20targeted%20cyberespionage%20campaign.%20The%20breaches%20have%20been%20mitigated%2C%20as%20per%20the%20officials%2C%20but%20an%20FBI%20investigation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20US%20government%20official%20told%20reporters%20it%20would%20be%20unfair%20to%20compare%20it%20to%20the%20SolarWinds%20compromise%2C%20a%20sweeping%20set%20of%20digital%20break-ins%20that%20were%20disclosed%20in%20late%202020%20and%20blamed%20on%20Russian%20cyberspies%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20intrusion%20should%20not%20be%20compared%20to%20SolarWinds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said%2C%20calling%20the%20recently%20discovered%20campaign%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20narrower.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20official%20said%20he%20could%20not%20comment%20on%20Microsoft's%20decision%20to%20attribute%20the%20hack%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20hacking%20group%20forged%20digital%20authentication%20tokens%20to%20access%20webmail%20accounts%20running%20on%20the%20firm's%20Outlook%20service.%20The%20activity%20began%20in%20May%2C%20Microsoft%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20with%20any%20observed%20nation-state%20actor%20activity%2C%20Microsoft%20has%20contacted%20all%20targeted%20or%20compromised%20organisations%20directly%20via%20their%20tenant%20admins%20and%20provided%20them%20with%20important%20information%20to%20help%20them%20investigate%20and%20respond%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20did%20not%20say%20which%20organisations%20or%20governments%20had%20been%20affected%20but%20added%20that%20the%20hacking%20group%20involved%20primarily%20targets%20entities%20in%20Western%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20embassy%20in%20London%20called%20the%20accusation%20%26quot%3Bdisinformation%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20the%20US%20government%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20biggest%20hacking%20empire%20and%20global%20cyber%20thief.%26quot%3B%20China%20routinely%20denies%20involvement%20in%20hacking%20operations%20regardless%20of%20the%20available%20evidence%20or%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20Adam%20Hodge%20said%20an%20intrusion%20in%20Microsoft's%20cloud%20security%20%26quot%3Baffected%20unclassified%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20without%20elaborating%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOfficials%20immediately%20contacted%20Microsoft%20to%20find%20the%20source%20and%20vulnerability%20in%20their%20cloud%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hodge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20%26quot%3Bdetected%20anomalous%20activity%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btook%20immediate%20steps%20to%20secure%20our%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20department%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20Commerce%20Department%20said%20it%20took%20%26quot%3