e%20disruptive%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20weather%20pattern%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20discussing%20a%20plan%20to%20ban%20exports%20of%20all%20non-Basmati%20rice%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20That's%20because%20of%20rising%20domestic%20prices%20and%20authorities%20want%20to%20avoid%20the%20risk%20of%20more%20inflation%2C%20said%20the%20people%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20information%20is%20not%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20implemented%2C%20a%20ban%20would%20affect%20about%2080%25%20of%20India's%20rice%20exports.%20Such%20a%20move%20may%20lower%20domestic%20prices%2C%20but%20it%20risks%20sending%20global%20costs%20even%20higher.%20Rice%20is%20a%20staple%20for%20about%20half%20of%20the%20world's%20population%2C%20with%20Asia%20consuming%20about%2090%25%20of%20global%20supply.%20Benchmark%20prices%20have%20already%20soared%20to%20a%20two-year%20high%20on%20fears%20that%20the%20return%20of%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20will%20damage%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22f6o3vf6o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ff6o3vf6o_india-share-in-rice-exportbloomberg_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20accounts%20for%20about%2040%25%20of%20the%20global%20rice%20trade%20and%20has%20sought%20to%20tighten%20exports%20of%20some%20varieties.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20banned%20broken%20rice%20exports%20and%20imposed%20a%2020%25%20duty%20on%20shipments%20of%20white%20and%20brown%20rice%20after%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20sent%20prices%20of%20food%20staples%20like%20wheat%20and%20corn%20soaring.%20The%20country%20has%20also%20restricted%20wheat%20and%20sugar%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20food%2C%20trade%20and%20finance%20ministries%20didn't%20respond%20to%20emails%20or%20text%20messages%20seeking%20comment.%20India%20supplies%20rice%20to%20more%20than%2