es%20have%20been%20created%20in%20five%20regions%20of%20Ladakh%20as%20part%20of%20disengagement%20talks%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20clash%20at%20Galwan%20in%20June%202020%20and%20the%20subsequent%20build-up%20of%20Chinese%20and%20Indian%20armies%20along%20the%20disputed%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC).%20The%20buffer%20zones%20are%20in%20Galwan%2C%20the%20north%20and%20south%20banks%20of%20Pangong%20Tso%2C%20PP-17%20A%2C%20and%20in%20PP-15.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Stanzin%2C%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20pitched%20four%20tents%20just%20below%20Table%20Top%20mountain%20in%20Chushul.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20falls%20under%20a%20buffer%20zone.%20Then%20how%20did%20those%20tents%20come%20up%3F%20It%20is%20a%20complete%20violation%20of%20the%20disengagement%20agreement.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689240546000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F29195352%2F2020_9img27_Sep_2020_PTI27-09-2020_000180B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpla-tents-ladakh-buffer-zone%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chushul%20councillor%20Konchok%20Stanzin%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Breceived%20information%20from%20the%20villagers%20that%20while%20three%20tents%20were%20removed%20after%20the%20Indian%20Army%20objected%20to%20their%20presence%2C%20a%20fourth%20one%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20removed%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpla-tents-ladakh-buffer-zone%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Don't%20Leave%20House%20If...%5C%22%3A%20Kejriwal%20Makes%20A%20Request%20Amid%20Delhi%20Flooding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERequesting%20Delhiites%20residing%20in%20flood%20affected%20areas%20to%20not%20leave%2