%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20flood%20situation%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20Delhi%20has%20ordered%20all%20government%20and%20private%20schools%20in%20low-lying%20areas%20to%20close%20immediately%20without%20waiting%20for%20orders%20where%20there%20is%20a%20danger%20of%20flood%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandgi%20Ram%20Akhada%20Chowk%20area%20of%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%20witnessed%20severe%20flooding%20due%20to%20rise%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20low-lying%20areas%20of%20the%20city%20are%20still%20under%20water%20as%20the%20water%20level%20in%20Yamuna%20continues%20to%20rise%20following%20heavy%20rainfall%20and%20the%20release%20of%20water%20from%20the%20Hathnikund%20Barrage%20in%20neighbouring%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20water%20level%20of%20Yamuna%20and%20the%20resultant%20inundation%20of%20low-lying%20areas%2C%20traffic%20movement%20has%20been%20impaired%20in%20several%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20according%20to%20official%20inputs%2C%20the%20movement%20of%20commercial%20vehicles%20will%20be%20regulated%20as%20non-destined%20commercial%20vehicles%20won't%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20Delhi%20and%20will%20be%20diverted%20to%20the%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20Peripheral%20Expressways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommercial%20vehicles%20will%20be%20diverted%20from%20Mukarba%20Chowk%2C%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%2C%20Ghazipur%20border%2C%20and%20from%20Akshardham%20towards%20DND.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20further%20said%20no%20commercial%20vehicles%20will%20be%20allowed%20between%20Mukarba%20Chowk%20and%20Wazirabad%20Bridge%2C%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%20and%20IP%20Flyover%2C%20and%20Akshardham%20and%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20has%20forecasted%20light%20to%20moderate%20intensity%20rain%20in%20South-West%20Delhi%20and%20adjoining%20areas%