ithium%20Mining%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13124126%2Fbattery-g6f2cb070e_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20Cabinet%20has%20reportedly%20cleared%20amendments%20to%20the%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Act%2C%201957%2C%20to%20allow%20commercial%20mining%20of%20lithium%20and%20other%20critical%20minerals%20including%20beryllium%2C%20titanium%2C%20niobium%2C%20tantalum%20and%20zirconium.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20private%20companies%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20mine%20these%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minerals%20in%20question%20are%20key%20to%20the%20production%20of%20mobile%20phones%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20solar%20panels%2C%20semiconductors%20and%20wind%20turbines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20mineral%20blocks%20%5Bof%20these%20critical%20minerals%5D%20will%20be%20auctioned%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20aware%20of%20the%20developments%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fcabinet-approves-lithium-auction-process%2Farticle67071797.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%3Eusinessline%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Funion-cabinet-clears-commercial-mining-of-lithium-5-other-critical-minerals%2F1666679%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20once%20Parliament%20clears%20the%20amendments%2C%20the%20government%20will%20be%20able%20to%20grant%20a%20single%20exploration%20licence%20to%20companies%20through%20such%20auctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20single%20exploration%20licence%20will%20encourage%20more%20private%20investment%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20where%20currently%20private%20presence%20is%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20government%20source%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%