r%20the%20right%20opportunity%20which%20I%20got%20recently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20degree%2C%20she%20joined%20a%20rescue%20company%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20started%20working%20as%20a%20veterinarian.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Mangaluru%20with%20my%20husband%20who%20had%20a%20clinic%20there.%20He%20was%20helping%20out%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20forest%20department%2C%20which%20gave%20me%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20get%20into%20onfield%20rescuing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20nearly%20two%20years%20since%20Meghana%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F122995%2Ffed-delays-26-year-old-creates-app-helps-rescue-animals-real-time%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erescuing%20wild%20animals.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20has%20assisted%20the%20forest%20department%20on%20several%20missions%20and%20has%20rescued%20eight%20leopards%2C%20bringing%20them%20home%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJumping%20in%20wells%20%26amp%3B%20climbing%20building%20is%20a%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20duty%20call%20for%2024%20hours%2C%20it%20is%20the%20passion%20for%20wildlife%20that%20keeps%20the%20veterinarian%20going.%20She%20has%20been%20in%20rescue%20missions%20which%20entail%20risks%20for%20both%20her%20and%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20the%20animal%20is%20always%20my%20top%20priority.%20Leopards%20are%20frequently%20the%20ones%20we%20rescue%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20they%20are%20just%20as%20afraid%20of%20us%20as%20we%20are%20of%20them.%20There%20are%20significant%20risks%20of%20injury%20for%20both%20myself%20and%20the%20animal%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghana%20adds%20that%20when%20she%20is%20on%20a%20rescue%20mission%2C%20she%20does%20not%20even%20think%20for%20a%20second%20before%20risking%20her%20life%20to%20save%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Dinesh%20Kumar%20Y%20K%2C%20the%20deputy%20conservator%20of%20forests%20(DCF)%20of%20Mangaluru%20division%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20on%20several%20missions%20with%20Meghana%20says%20the%20same.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20very%20light-footed%20and%20quick-witted%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20her%20work.%20She%20does%20not%20even%20blink%20before%20jumping%20into%20wells%20and%20climbing%20floors%20of%20buildings%20to%20save%20the%20animal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meghana%20had%20to%20jump%20in%20a%2020%20feet%20well%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323632%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20had%20to%20jump%20in%20a%20well%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%20that%20was%20stuck%20in%20it%20for%20days.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Meghana%20Pemmaiah%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20forest%20department%20is%20always%20short%20of%20such%20rescuers%20and%20Meghana%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20has%20been%20helping%20us%20in%20missions.%20The%20animals%20are%20usually%20found%20in%20encroached%20forest%20land%2C%20stuck%20in%20wells%2C%20and%20sometimes%20in%20households.%20This%20puts%20the%20life%20of%20the%20animal%20and%20the%20surrounding%20people%20in%20jeopardy.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20plan%20and%20execute%20everything%20very%20carefully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dangerous%20yet%20thrilling%20incident%20recently%2C%20Meghana%20had%20to%20jump%20into%20a%2020-feet-deep%20well%20at%20Niddodi%20in%20Dakshina%20Kannada%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%20stuck%20in%20it%20for%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20well%20was%20quite%20deep%20and%20we%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20leopardess.%20The%20only%20option%20was%20to%20jump%20inside%20to%20sedate%20her%20and%20carry%20her%20up.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20I%20was%20put%20in%20a%20cage%20and%20lowered%20into%20the%20well.%20I%20darted%20at%20the%20leopardess%20at%20close%20range%20and%20waited%20until%20she%20was%20sedated.%20I%20dragged%20her%20into%20my%20cage%20afterwards%20and%20the%20team%20pulled%20us%20both%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghana%20took%20the%20animal%20under%20her%20care%2C%20examining%20it%20for%20injuries%20and%20providing%20treatment.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20animals%20are%20kept%20under%20observation.%20When%20they%20become%20fit%2C%20we%20take%20them%20to%20their%20real%20home%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wilderness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20animal-human%20conflict%20regularly%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F95504%2Fanimal-conservation-human-livelihoods-balance-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20animal%20and%20human%20conflict%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eshe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20rapid%20urbanisation%20and%20expansion%20of%20cit