e%20importance%20of%20using%20these%20fruits%2C%20Digvijay%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20philosophy%20behind%20the%20move%20to%20using%20Indian%20native%20fruits%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20to%20give%20them%20the%20importance%20they%20deserve.%20With%20my%20generation%2C%20we%20sometimes%20tend%20to%20forget%20the%20culturally%20rich%20country%20and%20its%20diverse%20flora%20and%20fauna.%20You%20know%20how%20our%20grandparents%20would%20tell%20us%20that%20they%20would%20just%20pick%20up%20fruits%20straight%20from%20trees%20and%20eat%20them%E2%80%A6we%20never%20got%20that%20chance.%20Using%20these%20fruits%20is%20a%20very%20small%20step%20but%20I%20want%20to%20introduce%20my%20generation%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20chocolates%20are%20available%20to%20buy%20from%20Saraam%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saraam.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsaraam.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stores%20in%20Udaipur%20and%20Jaipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689170288000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-12T174705.966-1689164237.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323561%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Udaipur%20resident%20Digvijay%20Singh%20is%20a%20self-taught%20chocolatier%20who%20runs%20Saraam%2C%20a%20bean%20to%20bar%20company%20that%20incorporates%20indigenous%20fruits%20like%20ice%20apple%2C%20kokum%2C%20baer%20and%20more%20in%20delicious%20chocolate%20slabs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F3235