%20to%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIMD%20has%20issued%20a%20fresh%20red%20and%20orange%20alert%20in%20Himachal%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20red%20alert%20has%20been%20issued%20for%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20Solan%2C%20Shimla%2C%20Sirmaur%2C%20Kullu%2C%20Mandi%2C%20Kinnaur%2C%20and%20Lahaul%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours.%20An%20orange%20alert%20has%20been%20issued%20in%20Una%2C%20Hamirpur%2C%20Kangra%2C%20and%20Chamba.%20A%20flash%20flood%20warning%20has%20been%20issued%20for%20Mandi%2C%20Kinnaur%2C%20and%20Lahaul-Spiti%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20IMD%20Scientist%20Sandeep%20Kumar%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20on%20Monday%20and%20took%20stock%20of%20the%20situation.%20Sukhu%20has%20sought%20assistance%20from%20the%20centre.%20He%20recently%20headed%20a%20review%20meeting%20of%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(SDMA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20is%20now%20on%20evacuating%20300%20stranded%20tourists%20and%20residents%20at%20Chandertaal%2C%20tweeted%20the%20CM.%20He%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20state%20has%20not%20seen%20such%20rains%20in%20the%20past%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20videos%20of%20the%20devastation%20have%20been%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%2C%20what%20also%20stands%20out%20is%20the%20heroic%20efforts%20by%20the%20police%2C%20NDRF%2C%20SDRF%2C%20ITBP%2C%20officials%20as%20well%20as%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20heroes%20risking%20their%20lives%20to%20save%20others%20in%20dire%20conditions%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305165%2Fiit-mandi-researchers-devise-test-to-assess-earthquake-resistance-in-himalayan-region-buildings%2F%5C%22%20t