se%20and%20recycle%20water%20to%20create%20a%20green%20oasis%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20desert.%20We%20believe%20that%20sustainable%20development%20is%20important%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akanksha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Outdoor%20spaces%20to%20learn%20in%20and%20from%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20uses%20the%20vegetation%20and%20natural%20features%20of%20the%20school%20to%20its%20advantage%2C%20with%20trees%20becoming%20the%20focal%20points%20within%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20design.%20%E2%80%9CNinety%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20trees%20on%20the%20property%20were%20saved%20from%20being%20chopped%20down.%20The%20school%20campus%20moves%20around%20the%20trees%20and%20vegetation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trees%20grow%20throughout%20the%20building%2C%20creating%20transitional%20spaces%20between%20classroom%20clusters%2C%20courtyards%2C%20activity%20zones%2C%20walkways%2C%20and%20congregational%20areas%2C%20providing%20a%20green%20and%20refreshing%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20created%20various%20outdoor%20spaces%20for%20the%20students%20to%20learn%20in%20and%20from.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20have%20outdoor%20classrooms%20to%20encourage%20students%20to%20observe%2C%20learn%20and%20interact%20with%20their%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20aims%20to%20bring%20the%20students%20close%20to%20nature.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20has%20outdoor%20classrooms%2C%20a%20rainwater%20harvesting%20channel%2C%20and%20a%20terrace%20that%20opens%20to%20tree%20tops.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Akanksha%20Gupta%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cafeteria%20of%20the%20school%20stands%20beside%20a%20gardening%20patch%20next%20where%20students%20can%20understand%20where%20the%20food%20they%20consume%20comes%20from%2C%20while%20also%20helping%20take%20care%20of%20the%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20land%20had%20a%20channel%20of%20water%20running%20through%20it%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20restore%20it.%20The%20school%20also%20has%20a%20plantation%20area%20where%20they%20grow%20their%20food%20and%20the%20produce%20is%20utilised%20in%20the%20cafeteria%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20also%20has%20a%20very%20unique%20play%20area%20on%20the%20terrace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20building%20was%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20the%20terrace%20of%20the%20building%20comes%20at%20par%20with%20the%20treetops.%20The%20terrace%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20nature%20with%20leaves%20peeking%20out%20of%20punctures%20in%20the%20floorplate%2C%20allowing%20children%20the%20opportunity%20to%20play%20among%20the%20treetops%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akanksha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20are%20free%20to%20climb%20the%20trees%20and%20pluck%20the%20produce%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20gives%20them%20a%20space%20to%20live%20a%20childhood%20that%20is%20much%20more%20than%20just%20gadgets%20and%20television.%20The%20environment%20that%20they%20might%20see%20on%20screens%20is%20a%20reality%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saurabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20sustainability%20out%20of%20textbooks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20building%20complements%20and%20blends%20into%20the%20greenery%20on%20the%20grounds%2C%20the%20building%20materials%20sing%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CPreserving%20the%20existing%20nature%20was%20one%20of%20our%20first%20goals%20while%20designing%20the%20property.%20There%20were%20fruit%20trees%20such%20as%20mango%20and%20jamun%2C%20which%20are%20still%20growing%20on%20the%20grounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20materials%2C%20the%20duo%20tried%20to%20upcycle%2C%20recycle%20and%20reduce%20waste%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20place%20is%20so%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature%2C%20the%20materials%20had%20to%20be%20too.%20All%20the%20steel%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20building%20is%20upcycled%20and%20locally%20sourced.%20On%20the%20facade%20of%20the%20building%2C%20we%20used%20exposed%20brickwork.%20The%20reason%20was%20that%20it%20is%20fairly%20permanent%20in%20nature%20so%20the%20life%20cycle%20of%20the%20building%20increases.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20keep%20painting%20it%20up%20every%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311532%2Fbengaluru-betweenlines-sustainable-home-breathe-eco-friendly-earth-house-energy-efficient%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20idea%20of%20sustainability%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20school%20is%20a%20zero-waste%20campus%20that%20has%20a%20sewage%20disposal%20system%2C%20and%20harvests%201.5%20lakh%20litres%20of%20rainwater%20besides%20children%20growing%20their%20own%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Outdoor%20classroom%20in%20EuroSchool%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323070%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20outdoor%20classroom%20in%20EuroSchool%20Bannerghatta.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Akanksha%20Gupta%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheetalakshmi%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%2C%20believes%20that%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20bring%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20to%20life.%20%E2%80%9CA%20sustainable%20world%2C%20filled%20with%20the%20blessings%20and%20bounty%20of%20nature%2C%20is%20the%20best%20gift%20we%20can%20leave%20behind%20for%20future%20generations.%20At%20school%20we%20subtly%20sensitise%20students%20about%20the%20environment%20through%20hands-on%20and%20thought-provoking%20activities%2C%20by%20incorporating%20them%20into%20their%20curriculum%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%2