nth%2C%20I%20visit%20our%20home%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20stay%20there%20for%20a%20week.%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20save%20water%20by%20reusing%20it%20for%20toilet%20flushing%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229847%2Fgardening-tips-natural-greywater-recycling-indukanth-ragade-save-water-chennai-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eirrigating%20my%20crop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20without%20the%20guilt%20%5Bof%20wastage%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Need%20more%20competitors%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20entrepreneurs%2C%20Abhijit%20wishes%20for%20more%20competitors%20in%20the%20market.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20hardly%20any%20dedicated%20company%20or%20individual%20working%20in%20this%20sector.%20We%20need%20similar%20products%20coming%20in%20the%20market%20so%20that%20more%20innovative%20ways%20are%20given%20thought%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhijit%20explains%20that%20greywater%20comprises%20up%20to%2075%25%20of%20daily%20water%20use.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F